channel.title: Gone for 2 Weeks.... See ya soon :)
channel.description: So, this June 3 (+8:00 GMT), I along with my family will be heading to the US West Coast to have a tour. If there's gonna be a new update for Black Mesa or any news or something, feel free to post here.. I might be able to communicate if I have the time to do so while I'm there. :slight_smile: Wish for us a safe trip until we get home.
